import React from 'react'
import TextField from '@material-ui/core/TextField'

class Login extends React.Component{
 render() {
     return(
         <form>
             <TextField
                label="Email"
                placeholder="Your Email"
                margin="normal"
             />
             <TextField
                label="Password"
                placeholder="Your Email"
                margin="normal"
             />
         </form>
     )
 }   
}
export default Login
